-
-**Declaración pom.xml**
-
-```xml
-<dependency>
-  <groupId>com.elrosado</groupId>
-  <artifactId>jlib-pubsub</artifactId>
-  <version>1.0.0</version>
-</dependency>
-```
-
-**Configuración application.yml**
-
-```yaml
-# Equivalente a appsettings.json: PubSubSettings
-pubsub:
-  project-id: ${GCP_PROJECT_ID}
-  topic: ${PUBSUB_TOPIC:}
-  subscription: ${PUBSUB_SUBSCRIPTION:}
-```
-
-> Topics y subscriptions **no se crean desde código** — es responsabilidad de IaC (Terraform).
